steps.html_instructions: Head west on W 400 S/W University Blvd toward S Main St
Take the 1st right onto W 500 S/Cesar E. Chavez Blvd
Take the I-80 E/I-80 W ramp on the left to Las Vegas/Cheyenne/Reno/S.L. International Airport
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-15 S/Las Vegas/I-80 E/Cheyenne and merge onto I-15 S/I-80 E

Keep right at the fork to continue on I-80 E, follow signs for Cheyenne/Interstate 80
Entering Wyoming
Take exit 211 for Wyoming 789 N toward Interstate 80 Business/U.S. 287/Rawlins
Turn left onto U.S. 287 N/WY-789 N/3rd St (signs for Wyoming 789/Casper-Lander)

Turn right to merge onto I-90 E toward Moorcroft
Entering South Dakota
Take exit 30 for U.S. 14 Alternate W/S Dakota 34 E/S Dakota 79 N toward Lazelle St/Deadwood-Lead

Turn left onto SD-34 E/Boulder Canyon Rd/Lazelle St
Continue to follow SD-34 E
S Pierre St turns right and becomes E Pleasant Dr

Turn left onto S Euclid Ave
Destination will be on the left
